---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Professional Liability Insurance | E&O Coverage | PCFG Insurance" description="Protect your professional reputation with E&O insurance from PCFG. Coverage for errors, omissions, and negligence claims. Free quote for consultants and professionals." keywords="professional liability insurance, E&O insurance, errors and omissions, malpractice insurance, consultant insurance">
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-900 via-navy-800 to-navy-700 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">Professional Liability Insurance</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-navy-300 mb-8">Errors & Omissions (E&O) Coverage</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 mb-8">
          You made a <span class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">$50,000 mistake</span>. Your client is suing. 
          Can you afford the defense costs—even if you did nothing wrong?
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/commercial-quote" class="bg-yellow-600 hover:bg-yellow-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
            Get a Free E&O Quote
          </a>
          <a href="tel:877-717-7234" class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white border-2 border-white/30 px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
            Call (877) 717-7234
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- The Problem Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">When Professional Advice Goes Wrong</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          A management consultant gave advice that led to a client's failed expansion. The client lost $2 million and sued for professional negligence.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          The consultant's advice was sound. The client ignored key recommendations. But the lawsuit still cost <strong>$75,000 in legal fees</strong> to defend—and that was before a $25,000 settlement to make it go away.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 mb-6">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700">Total cost: $100,000</p>
          <p class="text-xl text-red-600 mt-2">The consultant's general liability policy? Paid $0.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Professional mistakes aren't covered by standard business insurance. That's the gap that puts your personal assets—and your reputation—at risk.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Statistics Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">The Reality of Professional Liability</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">1 in 5</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">professionals face a claim each year</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">$50K+</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">average defense costs—even for frivolous claims</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">$150K+</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">average settlement when cases mediate</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">$0</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">paid by general liability for professional services</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Coverage Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">What E&O Insurance Covers</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Covered Claims -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-6">Covered Claims</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Errors & Mistakes</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Calculation errors, missed deadlines, documentation mistakes</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Omissions & Negligence</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Failure to recommend, missing information, bad advice</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Misrepresentation</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">False promises, exaggerated capabilities, misleading statements</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Personal Injury</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Libel, slander, copyright infringement in professional context</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- What Policy Pays -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-6">What the Policy Pays</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Legal Defense Costs</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Attorney fees ($300-500/hour), expert witnesses, court costs</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Settlements & Judgments</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Negotiated settlements, court judgments, arbitration awards</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Disciplinary Proceedings</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">License board defense, professional association hearings</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Who Needs It -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">Who Needs Professional Liability Insurance?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <strong>If you provide advice, expertise, or specialized services for a fee, you need E&O coverage.</strong>
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-3">💼 Consultants</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• Management consultants</li>
            <li>• IT consultants</li>
            <li>• Marketing consultants</li>
            <li>• HR consultants</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-3">💻 Technology</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• Software developers</li>
            <li>• Web designers</li>
            <li>• Systems integrators</li>
            <li>• IT project managers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-3">💰 Financial</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• Financial advisors</li>
            <li>• Accountants & CPAs</li>
            <li>• Bookkeepers</li>
            <li>• Tax preparers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-3">🏠 Real Estate</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• Real estate agents</li>
            <li>• Property managers</li>
            <li>• Appraisers</li>
            <li>• Mortgage brokers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-3">⚖️ Legal & Professional</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• Insurance agents</li>
            <li>• Architects</li>
            <li>• Engineers</li>
            <li>• Interior designers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-3">🎨 Creative</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• Graphic designers</li>
            <li>• Marketing agencies</li>
            <li>• PR firms</li>
            <li>• Photographers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Real World Scenarios -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">Real-World E&O Claim Scenarios</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Scenario 1 -->
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-900 mb-4">The IT Consultant's Oversight</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            An IT consultant configured a client's cloud backup incorrectly. When ransomware hit, backups were corrupted. Client lost 6 months of financial data and sued for $500,000.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">Without E&O:</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">$85K legal fees + $200K settlement = $285K (3 years of profit)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">With E&O:</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Defense fully covered. Consultant paid only $5K deductible.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Scenario 2 -->
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-900 mb-4">The Financial Advisor's Alleged Misrepresentation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            A financial advisor recommended an investment that underperformed. Client claimed "guaranteed returns" were promised and sued for $1.2M.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">Without E&O:</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">$150K legal fees before dismissal. Nearly lost practice.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">With E&O:</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Defense costs fully covered. Business survived.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Cost Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">E&O Insurance Costs vs. Risk</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">Typical annual premiums:</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b pb-3">
            <span class="text-gray-700">Small consultant ($100K revenue)</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-navy-600">$1,500 - $3,000/year</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b pb-3">
            <span class="text-gray-700">Mid-size firm ($1M revenue)</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-navy-600">$5,000 - $15,000/year</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b pb-3">
            <span class="text-gray-700">10 years of premiums</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-navy-600">~$30,000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-gray-700">One claim without insurance</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-red-600">$200,000+</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4">
          <p class="text-green-800 font-semibold">Insurance isn't an expense—it's protection against catastrophic loss.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-900 to-navy-800 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Your Reputation Took Years to Build</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 mb-8">
        Don't let one mistake—or one difficult client—destroy what you've built. Even if you win in court, you lose financially without proper coverage.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/commercial-quote" class="bg-yellow-600 hover:bg-yellow-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
          Get Your E&O Quote
        </a>
        <a href="tel:877-717-7234" class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white border-2 border-white/30 px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
          Call (877) 717-7234
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
